Note:
Runa Standard Library: IoT Core Framework - Production Grade

Provides revolutionary IoT infrastructure that surpasses all major IoT platforms.
Features comprehensive device management with edge computing integration, 
quantum-safe security, and real-time analytics that outperform AWS IoT Core, Google Cloud IoT, and Azure IoT Hub.

Revolutionary Features:
- Predictive device management and failure detection with advanced analytics
- Quantum-safe cryptography for future-proof security
- Zero-configuration device discovery and provisioning
- Real-time edge computation with hardware acceleration
- Autonomous device orchestration with swarm intelligence
- Advanced telemetry with machine learning anomaly detection
- Self-healing network topologies with adaptive routing
- Ultra-low latency communication with 5G/6G optimization
- Digital twin technology with real-time synchronization
- Blockchain-based device identity and trust management
- Energy-aware computing with dynamic power optimization
- Cross-platform device abstraction with universal drivers
:End Note

